&lt;ul class=&quot;listtype-bullet listindent1 list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zfwz65zkz86zz66zwz73zz76zz79zz73zz85zz89zz88znwumz84zz88z29z76zgz84zz81zb2z122z7&quot;&gt;Own, build, and maintai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz81zz66z704z78zpz67zz75zf5wz66zpurtz86zmpw4z69z2wz87zbiaz88zz79z&quot;&gt;n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qowz82zfwz65zkz86zz66zwz73zz76zz79zz73zz85zz89zz88znwumz84zz88z29z76zgz84zz81zb2z122z7&quot;&gt; scalable data pipelines that connect various cloud data sources.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
